<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Underflow on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/underflow/</link><description>Recent content in Underflow on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/underflow/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C errno 34 ERANGE — Math result not representable</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/errno-34/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/errno-34/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-errno-34-erange--math-result-not-representable"&gt;[Solution] C errno 34 ERANGE — Math result not representable&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Math result not representable occurs when a system call fails and sets &lt;code&gt;errno&lt;/code&gt; to 34. This error indicates that the requested operation cannot be performed due to the specific condition described by ERANGE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Result of a math function is too large to represent (overflow).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Result is too small to represent as a non-zero value (underflow).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using exp() with a very large argument.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using pow() with arguments that produce huge results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;math.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;stdio.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;errno.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;string.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; errno &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;exp&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000.0&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (errno &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; ERANGE) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fprintf&lt;/span&gt;(stderr, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;exp(1000) overflow: %s (errno %d)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strerror&lt;/span&gt;(errno), errno);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;math.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;stdio.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;float.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000.0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; DBL_MAX_EXP) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fprintf&lt;/span&gt;(stderr, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;exp(%f) will overflow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, x);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;exp&lt;/span&gt;(x);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;printf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;exp(%f) = %f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, x, result);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/errno-33/"&gt;errno-33 EDOM&lt;/a&gt; — math argument out of domain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/errno-34/"&gt;errno-34 ERANGE&lt;/a&gt; — math result not representable (self).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/errno-12/"&gt;errno-12 ENOMEM&lt;/a&gt; — cannot allocate memory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::underflow_error - arithmetic underflow</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/underflow-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/underflow-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="stdunderflow_error---arithmetic-underflow"&gt;std::underflow_error - arithmetic underflow&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;std::underflow_error&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when a mathematical operation produces a value too close to zero to be represented. This is less common than overflow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Very small floating-point result
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;numeric_limits&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;::&lt;/span&gt;min() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2.0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Subnormal calculations
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1e-300&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; b &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1e-300&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; b; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// may underflow to zero
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Custom function throwing
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safe_sqrt&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; x) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;underflow_error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;negative&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;sqrt(x);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-before-operation"&gt;Fix 1: Check before operation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;abs(x) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;numeric_limits&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;::&lt;/span&gt;min()) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;underflow_error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;value too small&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-appropriate-types"&gt;Fix 2: Use appropriate types&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;static_cast&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;(a) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; b;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-catch-and-handle"&gt;Fix 3: Catch and handle&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; calculate(a, b);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;underflow_error&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;cerr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Underflow: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; e.what() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;endl;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/overflow-error-arithmetic/"&gt;std::overflow_error&lt;/a&gt; — arithmetic overflow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/domain-error-vector/"&gt;std::domain_error&lt;/a&gt; — math domain error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/range-error-base/"&gt;std::range_error&lt;/a&gt; — range error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::underflow_error — Arithmetic Underflow Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/underflow-error-2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/underflow-error-2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-stdunderflow_error--arithmetic-underflow-fix"&gt;[Solution] C++ std::underflow_error — Arithmetic Underflow Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;std::underflow_error&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when an arithmetic computation produces a result that is too close to zero to be represented accurately (floating-point underflow), or when a subtraction produces a result below the minimum representable value. It inherits from &lt;code&gt;std::runtime_error&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="why-stdunderflow_error-occurs"&gt;Why std::underflow_error Occurs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes include dividing very small floating-point numbers that underflow to zero, integer subtraction that wraps below minimum values, exponentiation with very small bases and large exponents, and chained multiplications of small values.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>